OL,3,CBBC admits to knowing about Scott
OL,4,CMills police investigation in 2017
OL,6,FThe BBC has admitted to knowing Scott
OL,7,FMills was being questioned by police
OL,8,Fin 2017, more than eight years before
OL,9,Fhe was sacked.
OL,11,F"We can confirm the BBC was made aware
OL,12,Fin 2017 of the existence of an ongoing
OL,13,Fpolice investigation, which was
OL,14,Fsubsequently closed in 2019 with no
OL,15,Farrest or charge being made. We are
OL,16,Fdoing more work to understand the
OL,17,Fdetail of what was known by the BBC at
OL,18,Fthis time," the BBC said in a
OL,19,Fstatement on Wednesday.
OL,26,@sD@AOUzD@KO]
