OL,3,CBBC admits to knowing about Scott
OL,4,CMills police investigation in 2017
OL,6,FThe organisation confirmed the DJ was
OL,7,Fsacked after it "obtained new
OL,8,Finformation" last week.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,F"What we can confirm is that in recent
OL,16,Fweeks, we obtained new information
OL,17,Frelating to Scott and we spoke
OL,18,Fdirectly with him. As a result, the
OL,19,FBBC acted decisively in line with our
OL,20,Fculture and values and terminated his
OL,21,Fcontracts on Friday 27 March".
OL,26,@wD@AOU
