OL,3,CBBC admits to knowing about Scott
OL,4,CMills police investigation in 2017
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police said on
OL,7,FTuesday that Mills was investigated in
OL,8,F2016 in relation to alleged "serious
OL,9,Fsexual offences against a teenage
OL,10,Fboy", telling ITV News the victim was
OL,11,Funder 16.
OL,13,FA Met Police spokesperson said they
OL,14,Fcouldn't confirm the specific age of
OL,15,Fthe victim due to the risk of jigsaw
OL,16,Fidentification.
OL,18,FThe revelation comes after Mills was
OL,19,Freportedly sacked from his BBC Radio 2
OL,20,Fjob on Monday over allegations
OL,21,Frelating to "personal conduct".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
