OL,3,CBBC admits to knowing about Scott
OL,4,CMills police investigation in 2017
OL,6,FMills has not publicly commented and
OL,7,Fwas last on air on Tuesday last week.
OL,9,F"The BBC has made a significant
OL,10,Fcommitment to improve its culture,
OL,11,Fprocesses and standards. Last year,
OL,12,Ffollowing an independent culture
OL,13,Freview, we set out the behavioural
OL,14,Fexpectations for everyone who works
OL,15,Fwith or for the BBC and we were clear
OL,16,Faction would be taken if these were
OL,17,Fnot met," the BBC added.
